<paragraph base="F9035644" id="IFRS02_43C"><paranum>43C</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 2"/><data name="paranum" value="43C"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS02_P0146">The entity settling a <xref base="SL141031" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0286">share&#x2011;based payment transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0351"/></ph></xref> when another entity in the group receives the goods or services shall recognise the transaction as an <xref base="SL141004" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0246">equity&#x2011;settled share&#x2011;based payment transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0106"/></ph></xref> only if it is settled in the entity&#x2019;s own <xref base="SL140998" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0243">equity instruments<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0102"/></ph></xref>. Otherwise, the transaction shall be recognised as a <xref base="SL140992" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0240">cash&#x2011;settled share&#x2011;based payment transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0032"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>